race.comment: Looks a strong race. GOLD MEDALLIST (6) resumes for her second campaign having gone unbeaten in four runs last time in, steadily rising through the grades, culminating in a BM70 win at Sandown Hillside. This is a fair ask first up against some smart types but we don't know her ceiling and she can measure up. IMMORTAL STAR (4) is in great form having won two of her past three. She came right away with a sharp turn of foot at Flemington last time, making full use of the 52kg there. She's up in the weights here but rates highly again. LAA DE SHA (1) won well fresh here, close up again last time at Flemington. He should be hard to hold out. PERILOUS FIGHTER (2) next in line.
